		"description": "<p>Just because you can win a fair fight doesn&rsquo;t mean you have to. Your potent combination of covert tricks and raw martial skill makes you an expert in sudden, explosive violence. You gain the following benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Your Strength or Dexterity score increases by 1, to a maximum of 20.</li>\n<li>You can use any weapon you are proficient with that lacks the heavy, two-handed, and versatile properties with @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.4727pnvz5nwn3h23]{Sneak Attack}.</li>\n<li>If you use @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.d8k1x28y4vn6h3q5]{Cunning Action} to take the Dash option and move more than 20 feet in a straight line, the next melee weapon attack you make this turn deals an additional 1d6 points of damage.</li>\n<li>You gain proficiency with improvised weapons.</li>\n</ul>",
